WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.752
Conflict is inevitable, but it is not always negative. When

00:00:04.752 --> 00:00:09.504
managed constructively, it maintains optimum stimulation and drives adaptive capabilities.

00:00:09.504 --> 00:00:14.256
Team breakdowns can be understood through a collapsing pyramid of

00:00:14.256 --> 00:00:19.008
dysfunctions. The foundation is an absence of trust, where true

00:00:19.008 --> 00:00:23.760
feelings are hidden. This immediately sparks the second dysfunction: a

00:00:23.760 --> 00:00:28.512
fear of conflict, leading to artificial harmony. Without productive debate,

00:00:28.512 --> 00:00:33.264
there is a lack of commitment and ambiguity. This causes

00:00:33.264 --> 00:00:38.016
an avoidance of accountability, and ultimately, inattention to results, where

00:00:38.016 --> 00:00:42.768
ego overrides collective success.
